<p>Wayne Rooney clearly not happy with his side, sending them out early. Harry Redknapp meanwhille has brought on Robbie Keane, Claude Makelele and Darren Fletcher.</p>

<p>Well the professional goalkeepers are off the pitch now and England have a couple more familiar faces coming on. Former internationals Joe Cole and Emile Heskey will feature for Wayne Rooney's side.</p>

<p>The former Tottenham boss is incharge of the ROTW, who have largely dominated this game.</p>

